def distance ( lat1 , lat2 , lon1 , lon2 ) :		      Disassembly of <code object distance at 0x7fbac0e8de40, file  Disassembly of <code object distance at 0x7f2b01639f60, file  script_not_found : None
    lon1 = radians ( lon1 )				      2 0 LOAD_GLOBAL 0 ( radians )				    2 0 LOAD_GLOBAL 0 ( radians )				  
    lon2 = radians ( lon2 )				      2 LOAD_FAST 2 ( lon1 )					    2 LOAD_FAST 1 ( lat2 )					  
    lat1 = radians ( lat1 )				      4 CALL_FUNCTION 1						    4 CALL_FUNCTION 1						  
    lat2 = radians ( lat2 )				      6 STORE_FAST 2 ( lon1 )					    6 STORE_FAST 2 ( lon1 )					  
    dlon = lon2 - lon1					      								    								  
    dlat = lat2 - lat1					      3 8 LOAD_GLOBAL 0 ( radians )				    3 8 LOAD_GLOBAL 0 ( radians )				  
    a = sin ( dlat / 2 ) ** 2 + cos ( lat1 ) * cos ( lat2 ) * 10 LOAD_FAST 3 ( lon2 )					    10 LOAD_FAST 1 ( lat2 )					  
    c = 2 * asin ( sqrt ( a ) )				      12 CALL_FUNCTION 1					    12 CALL_FUNCTION 1
